p: Compounds with monoisotopic masses 210.0890 Da (2) and 224.1046 Da (3 and 4) were tentatively identified as unknown phenolics ( Table 1). Other classes of phenolic compounds like flavonoids, galloylglucoses or ellagitannins that are characteristic to Eucalyptus plants ( Marsh et al., 2017) were not found in the LCP.
